# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Google OAuth client_id for the extension
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Create a Chrome-extension OAuth client (NOT "Web application") at:
#   https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#
# Steps:
#   1. Create / select a project
#   2. Enable the Gmail API under "APIs & Services" → "Library"
#   3. Configure the OAuth consent screen (External, add the Gmail scopes)
#   4. Credentials → Create credentials → OAuth client ID
#      Application type:  Chrome extension
#      Item ID:           your unpacked extension ID (chrome://extensions)
#   5. Copy the generated ...apps.googleusercontent.com value below
#
# Then build:
#   bun run build
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
